ckquote>\n<p>按这个教程来ok了： <a href=\"https://www.jianshu.com/p/c6c226d3c3f0\">CentOS7 忘记密码</a></p>\n<p>大致不走如下：</p>\n<h1 id=\"修改引导\"><a href=\"#修改引导\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"修改引导\"></a>修改引导</h1><p>修改这两处即可:</p>\n<img src=\"/post/CentOS7%20%E5%BF%98%E8%AE%B0%E5%AF%86%E7%A0%81%E5%90%8E%E4%BF%AE%E6%94%B9/SouthEast.png\" class=\"\" title=\"image\">\n<p>按 Ctrl+X 启动系统</p>\n<h1 id=\"进入shell\"><a href=\"#进入shell\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"进入shell\"></a>进入shell</h1><p>首先切换至 <code>root</code> 用户， 网上教程大多没有</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight shell\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">chroot /sysroot</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>再使用 <code>passwd root</code> 修改密码。</p>\n<p>最后 <code>touch /.autorelabel</code>, 在&#x2F;目录下创建一个.autorelabel文件，有这个文件存在，系统在重启时就会对整个文件系统进行relabeling。</p>\n<p>exit&amp;&amp;reboot</p>\n","text":" 网上的大部分教程都是坑。。 按这个教程来ok了： CentOS7 忘记密码 大致不走如下： 修改引导修改这两处即可: 按 Ctrl+X 启动系统 进入shel...","permalink":"/post/CentOS7 忘记密码后修改","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":265,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"CentOS7","slug":"CentOS7","count":1,"path":"api/categories/CentOS7.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"CentOS7","slug":"CentOS7","count":1,"path":"api/tags/CentOS7.json"},{"name":"忘记密码","slug":"忘记密码","count":1,"path":"api/tags/忘记密码.json"},{"name":"经验","slug":"经验","count":7,"path":"api/tags/经验.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E4%BF%AE%E6%94%B9%E5%BC%95%E5%AF%BC\"><span class=\"toc-text\">修改引导</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E8%BF%9B%E5%85%A5shell\"><span class=\"toc-text\">进入shell</span></a></li></ol>","author":{"name":"Weiba","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/24520686?v=4","link":"/","description":"啊 又忘了更新了！","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/xweiba","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","